  .content
    %h3 
      Preview Pane
    %p This is the preview pane. Click on the more button on an item to view more information.
    .message.info
      %h3 Helpful Tips
      <img src="/images/lightbulb_32.png" class="fl" />
      %p Click on the arrows to filter your vouches.
  .preview